<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Royal_Society_Prizes_for_Science_Books&action=edit&section=9.php.html" title="Edit section: 2006 Winner">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="2006_Winner">2006 Winner</span></h3>
<ul>
