<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Royal_Society_Prizes_for_Science_Books&action=edit&section=17.php.html" title="Edit section: Royal Society Young People's Book Prize">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Royal_Society_Young_People.27s_Book_Prize">Royal Society Young People's Book Prize</span></h2>
<p>This category is awarded to the best science writing for children.</p>
