<li><i>Science Investigations - Electricity</i> by John Farndon</li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Royal_Society_Prizes_for_Science_Books&action=edit&section=23.php.html" title="Edit section: 2006 Winner">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="2006_Winner_2">2006 Winner</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i>The Global Garden</i> by Kate Petty, Jennie Maizels, Corina Fletcher</li>
</ul>
